            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <!-- Module 1 -->
                <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 flex flex-col hover:border-indigo-400 transition">
                    <div class="bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-600 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-graduation-cap text-2xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Amasomo Rusange (General Lessons)</h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-slate-600 text-sm flex-grow">
                        <li class="flex items-start"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-indigo-500 mt-1 mr-2.5"></i> Amasomo 25 y'ibanze aherekejwe n'ibitabo byuzuye.</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-indigo-500 mt-1 mr-2.5"></i> Kumenya uko operating system y'imbere ikora.</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-indigo-500 mt-1 mr-2.5"></i> Gusobanukirwa n'ibikoresho byose bya telefone.</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-indigo-500 mt-1 mr-2.5"></i> Ibizamini bigufasha kwipima no kubona amanota.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <!-- Module 2 -->
                <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 flex flex-col hover:border-emerald-400 transition">
                    <div class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-600 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-screwdriver-wrench text-2xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Ishuri ry'Aba Tekinisiye (Technician School)</h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-slate-600 text-sm flex-grow">
                        <li class="flex items-start"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-emerald-500 mt-1 mr-2.5"></i> Ibigice 12 by'Amasomo yuzuye yo gusana telefone.</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-emerald-500 mt-1 mr-2.5"></i> Koresha Multimeter na DC Power Supply mu gushaka amakosa.</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-emerald-500 mt-1 mr-2.5"></i> Kwiga gusoldera ibice bya telefone (Charging ports, ICs).</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-emerald-500 mt-1 mr-2.5"></i> Kumenya andi makosa ya eMMC, storage n'umuyoboro w'umuriro.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <!-- Module 3 -->
                <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 flex flex-col hover:border-purple-400 transition">
                    <div class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-user-shield text-2xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Cyber Security (Umutekano ku Mbuga)</h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-slate-600 text-sm flex-grow">
                        <li class="flex items-start"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-purple-500 mt-1 mr-2.5"></i> Ibigice 8 bitandukanye byigisha kurinda telefone yawe.</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-purple-500 mt-1 mr-2.5"></i> Sobanukirwa Phishing, SSL Certificates, na Fake Websites.</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-purple-500 mt-1 mr-2.5"></i> Gukemura ibibazo by'ibitero by'abajura batandukanye.</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-purple-500 mt-1 mr-2.5"></i> Gufata Impamyabumenyi yo kurinda umutekano.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
